text: Zaldy Villa is a Filipino politician from the island province of Siquijor in Central Visayas Region in the Philippines. He is currently serves as a Governor of Siquijor. He was first elected as Governor of the province in 2013 and was re-elected in and 2016 and 2019. ==References== * * * * ==External links== *Province of Suquijor Official Website Category:Living people Category:Governors of Siquijor Category:PDP–Laban politicians Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
